jspecview.util
Class JDXDecompressor

java.lang.Object
  jspecview.util.JDXDecompressor

public class JDXDecompressor
extends java.lang.Object

JDXDecompressor contains static methods to decompress the data part of a JCAMP-DX spectra that have been compressed using DIF, FIX, SQZ or PAC formats. If you wish to parse the data from XY format see JSpecViewUtils.parseDSV(java.lang.String, double, double)

Author:
Christopher Muir, Debbie-Ann Facey, Khari A. Bryan, Prof Robert J. Lancashire
